Package org.nerd4j.csv.field.validator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCSVFieldValidator<V>
    Abstract implementation of the CSVFieldValidator interface that performs the expected behavior and modifies the CSVFieldProcessContext accordingly with the framework execution policy.
    CheckNumberRange<N extends Number & Comparable<N>>
    Implementation of the CSVFieldValidator interface that checks the given Number value to be within the requested interval.
    CheckRegEx
    Implementation of the CSVFieldValidator interface that checks the given String matches the given regular expression.
    CheckStringLength
    Implementation of the CSVFieldValidator interface that checks the given String length to be within the requested interval.
    EmptyCSVFieldValidator
    Represents an empty validator that never fails.
